# install lombok in system to supoort some featurs of Spring Boot

# Install Postman

A -> Student Info 
1.addNewStudent (POST Request) Student Url -> http://localhost:8888/v1/students
{firstName -> Ram
lastName  -> Kumar}
2.Get All students Url(Get Request) -> http://localhost:8888/v1/students 
3.Get Student By Id Url(Get Request) ->  http://localhost:8888/v1/students/studentID/{id}
4.Get Student By Name(Get Request)  ->  http://localhost:8888/v1/students/{FirstName or Last Name}

B -> Module Info
1.Create Module (POST Request) Student Url -> http://localhost:8888/v1/modules
{moduleName -> CSE
moduleDetails  -> This is CSE Modules which will discuss about data Structure}

2.Get All Modules (Get Request) ->  http://localhost:8888/v1/module/all
3.Get Module By Id(Get Request) ->  http://localhost:8888/v1/module/id/{id}
4.Get Module By Name(Get Request) -> http://localhost:8888/v1/module/name/{name}

5.Put Request for Enrollment ->  http://localhost:8888/v1/enrolments
{
    "studentId": "1",
    "moduleId": "1"
}

